---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Kitchen Renovations Woden | Established &amp; Premium Homes"
  description="Kitchen renovations in Woden — premium renovations and custom cabinetry for the valley's established, mature homes, with careful pre-1980 asbestos checks. ACT-licensed builders. Free quote."
  canonical="https://kitchenrenovationscanberra.com.au/woden/"
>
  <Fragment slot="head">
  </Fragment>

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <span class="hero-eyebrow">Woden &middot; Curtin &middot; Garran &middot; Hughes &middot; Mawson</span>
      <h1>Kitchen renovations in <span class="accent">Woden</span>.</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        The Woden Valley is established, central Canberra &mdash; mature,
        well-located homes that owners renovate to a high standard rather than
        sell. We deliver premium kitchens here: custom cabinetry, quality stone,
        considered design, and careful asbestos checks on the older stock.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a class="ph-cta btn btn-primary" href="/quote/" aria-label="Call us"><span aria-hidden="true">&#9742;</span> <span class="ph-text">Tap to call</span></a>
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/quote/">Get a free quote</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <span class="section-eyebrow">Why Woden</span>
      <h2>The Woden kitchen story.</h2>
      <div class="divider"></div>
      <div style="max-width: 65rem;">
        <h3>Established, central, and renovated to keep.</h3>
        <p>
          The Woden Valley &mdash; Curtin, Garran, Hughes, Mawson, Phillip,
          Chifley &mdash; is established, leafy, centrally located Canberra. These
          homes hold their value and owners tend to <strong>renovate to stay</strong>
          rather than move, which means kitchens here are usually a quality,
          design-led upgrade rather than a quick flip. We design and build for
          longevity: <a href="/services/custom-cabinetry/">custom cabinetry</a>,
          premium <a href="/services/benchtops/">stone and porcelain benchtops</a>,
          and a layout planned to last.
        </p>

        <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Pre-1980 stock &mdash; and the Mr Fluffy factor.</h3>
        <p>
          A real point of care in Woden: several of its suburbs are among the most
          affected by the ACT&rsquo;s <strong>Mr Fluffy loose-fill asbestos</strong>
          legacy &mdash; amphibole insulation installed in homes between 1968 and
          1980, with Curtin, Garran and parts of Hughes notably represented on the
          affected-properties history. On any home of that era we treat asbestos
          identification as a non-negotiable first step: suspect wall sheeting,
          floor backing, eaves and splashbacks are tested, and licensed removal is
          arranged before any demolition. We never disturb material we suspect
          contains asbestos &mdash; it is a legal and safety requirement, and we
          plan for it honestly up front.
        </p>

        <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Designing for mature homes.</h3>
        <p>
          Older Woden homes can have non-standard openings, sub-floor services
          that need re-routing, and rooms that were closed off in a way that
          doesn&rsquo;t suit modern living. This is where
          <a href="/services/kitchen-design/">design</a> earns its keep &mdash;
          we map the options, advise where wall changes need structural work and
          ACTPLA approval, and build cabinetry to the exact (often irregular)
          dimensions. Plumbing to <strong>AS/NZS 3500</strong> and electrical to
          <strong>AS/NZS 3000</strong>, by ACT-licensed trades and certified.
        </p>

        <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Premium finish, done properly.</h3>
        <p>
          Woden clients generally want a premium result &mdash; integrated
          appliances, a feature island, quality stone, considered lighting. We
          deliver that with compliant materials and proper trades, to one fixed
          price. The goal is a kitchen that still looks and works beautifully in
          fifteen years, which is exactly the horizon most Woden owners are
          planning for.
        </p>

        <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Typical Woden kitchen jobs.</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Premium full renovation of a 1970s Garran home, with pre-demolition asbestos clearance ($45K&ndash;$80K)</li>
          <li>Custom cabinetry and a quartzite or porcelain island in a Curtin home</li>
          <li>Heritage-sympathetic kitchen in an established Hughes home</li>
          <li>Design-led reconfiguration opening a closed kitchen to living areas</li>
          <li>Mawson family kitchen with butler&rsquo;s pantry and integrated appliances</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <h2>Other service areas.</h2>
      <div class="areas-grid">
        <a class="area-pill" href="/belconnen/">Belconnen</a>
        <a class="area-pill" href="/gungahlin/">Gungahlin</a>
        <a class="area-pill" href="/tuggeranong/">Tuggeranong</a>
        <a class="area-pill" href="/dickson/">Dickson</a>
        <a class="area-pill" href="/canberra-region/">All Canberra &amp; the ACT</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="cta-block">
        <h2>Free Woden kitchen quote.</h2>
        <p>Premium renovations, careful asbestos checks, design-led layouts. Fixed-price quotes.</p>
        <div class="hero-actions" style="justify-content:center;">
          <a class="ph-cta btn btn-primary" href="/quote/" aria-label="Call us"><span aria-hidden="true">&#9742;</span> <span class="ph-text">Tap to call</span></a>
          <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/quote/">Get a free quote</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
